{
  "id": "adv_main_01_09_05",
  "title": "星見編2章39話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "（ずっと、姉妹の距離感に悩んでいた）\n（縛り、縛られな関係を作ってしまった負い目があった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(For so long‚ I was worried about the distance between my sister and me.)\n(I also felt guilty for having built this codependent relationship.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.833333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "（でもそれは、ほんの少しの勇気で）\n（笑っちゃうぐらい簡単に解消できて――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But all it took was a little bit of courage)\n(to resolve the problem with laughable ease.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "（もしかしたらそれこそが）\n（「姉妹」という距離感だったのかな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(And maybe that very thing)\n(was the sense of distance called “sisterhood.”)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 20.966666666666665
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-multi-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 20.980478313405
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "えっほ、えっほ……みんな～、遅いよ～！\n置いてっちゃうぞ～ぃ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hee-hoo! Hee-hoo! Hey‚ guys! You’re too slow!\nWe’re leaving you behind!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "な……なんなんですの、あの子……\nこの前は早朝ランニング、あんなに嫌がってましたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-what is with that girl?\nUp until quite recently‚ she detested morning jogs!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "なんか今朝はすっごく幸せな夢を見られて\n目覚めが良かったんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She said she had a really good dream last night\nand woke up refreshed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.900000000000006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "はあ、はあ……ほんと、すごい気分屋……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* *huff* Seriously… Her moods change like the wind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.23333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ琴乃ちゃん\n楽しいし、いいんじゃないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ now‚ Kotono.\nAs long as she’s having fun‚ who cares?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.92834447224936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、うだうだ文句言われながら走られるより\nずっとマシかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "True. If the alternative is listening to her grumble and groan while we run‚\nthis is much better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.21167771021524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん……容赦ないなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei… you really don’t hold back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-multi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5211.677710215241,
          "startTime": 63.945011043548575
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 63.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……はあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.81167771021522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん……大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa… are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.37247134844459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん……だ、大丈夫、だよ……\n自分のペースで……走れる、から",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah… I’m… okay.\nI’ll run at… my own pace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.81113341649372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "お、お姉ちゃんも……心配しないで\nふたりとも……先、行ってていいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Saki‚ don’t worry… about me either.\nYou two can… go on ahead… of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.87149094304729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "わかったわ……無理しないでね……はぁ、はぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. Don’t hurt yourself‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.60482427638063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "（打ち合わせの日以来、千紗は少しだけ）\n（無理をしなくなった気がする）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Ever since the day of the meeting‚ Chisa has been just a little)\n(easier on herself.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.18006218633336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "（きっと、等身大の自分を受け入れ）\n（そんな自分に自信を持てたから……かもしれない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It must be because she accepted herself for who she is)\n(and she has confidence in herself… at least that’s my guess.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.21339551966658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん……何かあった？\n変わった、気がする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did something happen… to Chisa?\nShe seems… different.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.28006218633324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……きっと、変わったんだと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. I’m sure she did change.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.7467288529999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ、私も……\nもっと変わっていかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And that’s the very reason why\nI also have to change.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.0302206870046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "……沙季ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2302206870046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、なんでもありません\nそれより……私も少しペースを落とそうかと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Never mind. It’s nothing.\nActually‚ I think maybe I should slow down my pace a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.36035670003554,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "（……私もきっと、受け入れないといけない）\n（私自身も、妹離れしなくてはいけないのだと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I know I also need to accept the truth.)\n(I also need to distance myself a little from my sister.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.49369003336903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "（前に進んでいくと決めたあの子を、その決意を）\n（受け入れる準備をしなくてはいけない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(In order to respect her will to advance forward‚)\n(I need to be ready to accept her decision.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.96035670003567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……あ、あれ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* *huff* Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.56035670003567,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 144.56035670003567
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめんね\nやっぱり……ちょっと心配で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry.\nI just couldn’t stop worrying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.9558215654023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "また……一緒に走る？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Want to… run with me again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.2891548987356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、一緒に走る……でも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure. I’ll run with you. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.90548146924647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
