      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_05-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "「……打ち合わせ、出発がバラバラになっちゃって\nごめんね？　突然のことで心配したよね」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Sorry‚ our departure times for the meeting got all mixed up.\nThe sudden changes must have worried you.”",
