      "text": "「でも、ひとりで打ち合わせ、来られたじゃない\nだから千紗は、もっと自分に自信を持って大丈夫」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“But look at you‚ you made it to the meeting all by yourself.\nSo it’s okay for you to have a little more confidence in yourself‚ Chisa.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
