      "text": "「お姉ちゃんもね、今日、いろんなことがあったの\n私にも、乗り越えないといけないものが見つかった」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“You know‚ I went through a lot today‚ too.\nI also discovered an obstacle that I have to overcome.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
